These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: soul, pop, r&b, indie, gospel, funk, hip-hop
1. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of pop##1
2. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of indie##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
4. the fan of gospel is between the fan of soul and the fan of r&b##2
5. the fan of indie is between the fan of pop and the fan of soul##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | r&b | gospel | soul | indie | pop | funk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: writing, card-games, dancing, video-games, photography, rock-climbing, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is writing##2
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | sudoku | writing | dancing | video-games | card-games | photography |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: magic-tricks, collecting, chess, dancing, rock-climbing, cooking, singing
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is collecting##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Hobby   | singing | cooking | rock-climbing | collecting | magic-tricks | chess | dancing |

