2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is in the middle##1
7. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's hobby is singing##1
8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3    |      4      |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | puzzles | cooking | gardening | photography | baking | singing |

